<div class="container py-5">

    <p id="start">
        We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting the personal data you provide to us. This Privacy
        Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our car rental and sales
        website.
    </p>

    <div class="priv mb-4">
        <h2>1. Information We Collect:</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Full name</li>
            <li>Phone number</li>
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>Driver’s license information</li>
            <li>Residential address</li>
            <li>Payment details (e.g., credit card)</li>
            <li>Geolocation data (when necessary)</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="priv mb-4">
        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information:</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Process car rental or purchase requests</li>
            <li>Contact you regarding your booking or purchase</li>
            <li>Enhance your user experience on the website</li>
            <li>Send offers or updates (if you opt-in)</li>
            <li>Ensure safety and comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="priv mb-4">
        <h2>3. Data Protection:</h2>
        <p>
            We follow strict security procedures to protect your personal data from unauthorized access or misuse.
            All information is stored securely and encrypted where applicable.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="priv mb-4">
        <h2>4. Information Sharing:</h2>
        <p>
            We do <strong>not</strong> share your personal information with third parties, except in the following cases:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Payment processors for completing transactions</li>
            <li>Legal authorities when officially requested</li>
            <li>Insurance companies in case of accidents</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="priv mb-4">
        <h2>5. Cookies:</h2>
        <p>
            We use cookies to improve site performance and personalize your experience. You can disable cookies via
            your browser settings.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="priv mb-4">
        <h2>6. Your Rights:</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Request a copy of the data we hold about you</li>
            <li>Modify or correct your personal information</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your data at any time</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="priv mb-4">
        <h2>7. Policy Updates:</h2>
        <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted here, and your continued use
            of the site will be considered acceptance of those changes.
        </p>
    </div>

    <br>

    <p id="que" class="mt-4 fs-5">
        <strong>
            For any questions, please contact us at
            <a href="mailto:beyond_the_stack@gmail.com">beyond_the_stack@gmail.com</a>.
        </strong>
    </p>

</div>
